message.entry: Image From Workspace block does not support complex signals.
Constant value should not have more than 3 dimensions. For 4-D signal use Video From Workspace block.
User-defined floating point data types are not supported.
User-defined data type must have 0 Bias and SlopeAdjustmentFactor of 1.
Output data type must have word length less than or equal to 32 bits
If Value parameter is fixed-point, word length must be less than or equal to 32 bits
